  "text": "In addition to their key role in BA homeostasis, FXR activity and FGF19 signalling are involved in diverse biological pathways. Essentially, FXR exerts its functions by eliciting transcriptional alterations and controls a number of important metabolic pathways [CITATION_1] . In this section, we briefly review the key biological processes modulated by FXR and FGF19 with respect to their attractive therapeutic implications.",
